  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Somber, reverent, enveloped in slow-motion reverb tail. Low-register vowel space (O-U) with dark tilt and maximum release times. Each note hangs in the air like incense smoke. Conductor mode with a 45-second arc provides the gentlest possible crescendo \u2014 a requiem that builds so slowly it becomes meditation.",
